strings:
<voice_0x01001146><se_high>Carrie: I'm sorry, Cash.
This is all my fault.
<voice_0x01001147><se_high>Carrie: But I won't cry. I know you'd laugh if you saw me crying for you.

<voice_0x01001148><se_high>Carrie: No, I'll be strong for you, Cash. I'll take over
the casino and give it my all, I swear!
Just watch over me from heaven with Dad...
<voice_0x01001149><se_high>Carrie: Gaaaaah! He's back from the dead!
<voice_0x0100114A><se_def>Cash: Very funny. Spare us the theatrics, Carrie.
<voice_0x0100114B><se_def>Cash: I only got knocked out, for goodness' sake!

<voice_0x0100114C><se_high>Carrie: ‘Knocked out’!? More like ‘playing dead’!
I knew it, though. That's why I provoked you!
<voice_0x0100114D><se_def>Cash: Oh, you knew it, did you? Well, I was just testing to see if you'd actually feel any sadness at seeing me dead.

<voice_0x0100114E><se_high>Carrie: Of course I'd feel sad, you big jerk!
You're the only brother I have!

<voice_0x0100114F><se_def>Cash: You're right. After all, we've only got each other. I'd be sad to see you go, too.
But we're in over our heads here, kiddo.
<voice_0x01001150><se_def>Cash: If I hadn't shown up when I did, you'd have been toast!

<voice_0x01001151><se_high>Carrie: I'm sorry. I just...
I really wanted to win this time.
You're always ahead of me...

<voice_0x01001152><se_high>Carrie: But it's okay now.
I'll let you take Dad's place, Cash.

<voice_0x01001153><se_def>Cash: What's up with you, Carrie?
It isn't like you to give up so easily.

<voice_0x01001154><se_high>Carrie: You saved my life. So I'll let you win this time.
But don't expect me to make a habit of it.

<voice_0x01001155><se_high>Carrie: Look. We're almost at the Doors of Judgement.
Watch over my brother, everyone!

<voice_0x01001156><se_def>Cash: Oh, sis! How could this happen!?
But I won't forget your sacrifice, Carrie!
Not for as long as I live!

<voice_0x01001157><se_def>Cash: Don't you worry.
I'll take over Dad's place and make you proud.
<voice_0x01001158><se_def>Cash: I know you and Dad will be watching over me from heaven!
<voice_0x01001159><se_high>Carrie: Sorry, Cash, but I'm not dead yet!
<voice_0x0100115A><se_def>Cash: Ow!? Hey!
<voice_0x0100115B><se_def>Cash: So you're okay? I should have known better than to worry about you.
<voice_0x0100115C><se_high>Carrie: You big, fat cheater! I cannot BELIEVE you mixed sleeping powder in our food! You just threw the contest, as far as I'm concerned!

<voice_0x0100115D><se_high>Carrie: And look what happened!
You nearly got yourself killed!
You're lucky I found you in time!
<voice_0x0100115E><se_def>Cash: Look, I'm sorry.

<voice_0x0100115F><se_def>Cash: I just really wanted to win. To finally make
you respect me as an older brother.
But you know what? I don't care any more.

<voice_0x01001160><se_def>Cash: You risked your life to save me.
You deserve to become the sole heir.
<voice_0x01001161><se_high>Carrie: Huh!? Like...what are you saying?
<voice_0x01001162><se_def>Cash: I'm saying the fortune's yours. And let's make that the end of this stupid rivalry between us!
<voice_0x01001163><se_def>Cash: Anyway, we're almost at the Doors of Judgement. Bodyguards! We're still counting on you.
